File Sharing: Share larger files up to 500 MB! Conference Call: Connect with more friends in bigger conference calls up to 50 members. Call Performance: Improved call performance and connectivity. Bug Fixes: Bug fixes for a smoother experience.

Stickers: Make your chats more fun with stickers! Improved Call Connectivity: Enhanced call connectivity for quicker and better communication. Bug Fixes Enhancements: Enjoy a smoother and improved experience with various fixes and enhancements.

Call Link Generation: Effortlessly share unique call links for quick connections. Image Collage View: Simplified browsing through merged chat photos. Enhanced Control: Manage your online visibility choosing who sees you. Bug Fixes Enhancements: Enjoy a smoother and optimized experience.

Other party time during calls: Now shows the current time of the other party during audio calls. Improved Last Seen Functionality: Information on when contacts were last active has been enhanced for better accuracy. Extended Message character limit: Character limit for messages has been increased for longer messages. Bug Fixes and Improvements: Bug fixes and improvements made for better user experience.

Enhanced Contact Sharing: Share contact details using an improved contact card in chat. Forward Message Upgrade: Forward messages to up to 5 participants in a single action. Screen Sharing on Call: Share your screen during one on one calls for better communication. Auto Chat Backup: Automatically back up and restore chats for logged out sessions on the same device. Improved Call Quality: Enjoy smoother calls with enhanced call quality.

Improved Call Quality: Enjoy smoother calls with enhanced call quality.

Sound wave in voice notes: Visualize audio in voice notes for easier understanding. Improved call connectivity quality: Faster clearer calls with friends and family. Conference Call Optimization: Improved Conference Call feature for better communication. Bug Fixes and Improvements: Overall user experience enhancements.

Improved call connectivity on unstable networks

Conference Call : Added Conference Calling for up to 20 participants for high quality communication. Faster Message Delivery : Optimized message delivery for fast and reliable messaging. Enhanced File Sharing : Enhanced file sharing for quick and secure transmission of files. Bug fixes and performance improvements to enhance the overall app experience.
Bug Fixes and Improvements

Change Phone number: Change your phone number associated with your Comera account. Logout: Switch between existing or new accounts without uninstalling and reinstalling Comera. Permanent contacts: Save your Comera contacts in the server and retrieve them on a new device as permanent contacts. Nick Name: See the nicknames of unsaved contacts group participants for easy identification. Improved call connectivity quality: Experience better audio and video call quality with faster connectivity.

Change Phone number: Change your phone number associated with your Comera account. Logout: Switch between existing or new accounts without uninstalling and reinstalling Comera. Permanent contacts: Save your Comera contacts in the server and retrieve them on a new device as permanent contacts. Nick Name: See the nicknames of unsaved contacts group participants for easy identification. Improved call connectivity quality: Experience better audio and video call quality with faster connectivity.

Tag Participants: Tag participants in group chats for more interactive communication. Online Presence Indicator: See who s online with a visual indicator. Improved Call Stability: Calls are now more stable even on low bandwidth. Bug Fixes and UI Improvements: Improved experience with bug fixes and UI enhancements.

Users can now tap the group link or scan the QR code to join a group Improved call connectivity and call quality Improved message delivery time Contact Sync optimized Some minor bug fixes and improvements to the overall user experience

Listen to Voice Notes before Sending: Users can now listen to recorded voice notes before sending them. Read Receipt for Voice Notes: Users can know whether their voice note has been viewed and played. Play Voice Notes outside the Native Chat: A voice note will continue to play even when the user has navigated away from the native chat. Pause Continue Recording Voice Notes: Users can pause while recording voice notes and resume recording from the time it was paused. Feedback after Call: Users can share their call experience as feedback after ending a call. Bug Fixes Enhancements: Some minor bug fixes and improvements to the overall user experience.

Delete Multiple Messages: Users can delete multiple messages at a time. Enter is Send: Users can configure the Enter key to send messages. Group Chat Improvements: Members of a group chat have more options to interact with other members directly from the group. Bug Fixes Enhancements: Some minor bug fixes and improvements to the overall user experience.
Bug fixes and feature improvements.

Profile Status: Users can select from predefined status or create their own. Read Unread: Users can mark chats read or unread as per their needs. Improvements: Functional UI improvements for a better user experience.

Profile Status: Users can select from predefined status or create their own. Read Unread: Users can mark chats read or unread as per their needs. Improvements: Functional improvements for a better user experience.

Chat Backup: Create restore your chat backup whenever needed. Low Battery Alert: Comera will now alert the caller the callee in case of low battery. Latest features Improvements: A dedicated section created to share new developments. Security: Enhanced security for network communications. Improvements: Improvements made in contact syncing and other bugs fixes

Message Scheduler: Users can schedule messages to be sent at a specific date and time. Broadcast Messages: Users can broadcast messages to up to 25 contacts. Less Data for Calls: Users can opt for less data to be consumed for audio video calls.

Auto Download: Users can now control auto download of media on Wifi and data. Avatars: More avatars added to our avatars collection. Delete Account: The Delete Account feature and functionality have been further streamlined for better user experience Maintenance: Introduced performance improvements and bug fixes.

Avatar as Display Picture: Users can now set their Avatar as their Display Picture. Instant Media Sharing: Media can be captured and shared instantly from the home screen. Blocked Contacts: Stricter policies applied to Blocked Contacts. Report Contacts: Major tweaks to the Report Contact feature. Minor bug fixes.

View Once: Media files marked view once will be automatically deleted from the chat and won t be saved on the device after being viewed once. Media Preview and Editor: Comera users can now edit media files before sending them. In App Youtube videos: YouTube Videos can now be played directly in Comera. Minor Bug Fixes.

Custom Notification. Users can now set their favorite ringtone for messages and group message. Better Search. Users can search their image video link and Gifs using filter tags. Multiple bugs and crashes fixed.

Custom Notification. Users can now set their favorite ringtone for messages and group message. Better Search. Users can search their image video link and Gifs using filter tags. Multiple bugs and crashes fixed.

Disappearing messages. Users can now time their private messages which will disappear after the specified time adding more to user privacy. Better Search. Users can search their Audio and Document files using filter tags Push Notifications availability is improved Multiple bugs and crashes fixed.

Privacy options for User s Last Seen and Profile Photo. Voice note can now be played at 1.5x and 2x speed. Star message improvements. Simplified add edit remove process for display picture name and status. User can now remove display picture from the group. Bug fixes and refinements.

Privacy options for User s Last Seen and Profile Photo. Voice note can now be played at 1.5x and 2x speed. Star message improvements. Simplified add edit remove process for display picture name and status. User can now remove display picture from the group. Bug fixes and refinements.

You can now pin up to 3 conversations for instant accessibility. Export chats without media to other users. Star important messages to bookmark for later reference. Support for Arabic language added. UI refinements bug fixes and performance improvements. If you have any feedback or questions please navigate to Comera Settings Help Feedback or you can visit www.comeratech.com and chat with our representatives.

Call stability on network switching is improved. Call status messages are enhanced. Friend Requests and Friend List sections are added on Contact Screen. Call notifications are added to the chat screen. GSM and VoIP calls can be handled simultaneously now. Welcome banner added on new friend addition. Contacts UI has been improved. App crashes call bugs have been fixed.

The Comera app is updated regularly so that users can experience a better calling and messaging service. The latest release has several bug fixes and performance improvements. Get the latest version from the Appstore. Here s what s New: 1. Voice and video calling quality have been improved. 2. Call bugs have been fixed. 3. Voice and video call performance on poor internet conditions has been improved. 4. Chat experience reliability has been enhanced. 5. New updates will be automatically notified to the user by alerts. 6. Contacts searching has been made more user friendly. 7. Missed call notification and alerts will be displayed on the screen. 8. Application permission handling has been improved. 9. Swipe menu options are provided in the application.
